{{!
  CHARGEN CUSTOM TABS SNIPPET

  Adds the "Secret & Goal" tab to the chargen step list.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/components/chargen-custom-tabs.hbs

  IMPORTANT: This file might be empty or minimal if you don't have other custom chargen tabs.

  STEP 1: Check the file contents
  1. Open your game's ares-webportal/app/components/chargen-custom-tabs.hbs
  2. Look at what's in the file:
     - If it's EMPTY or has only comments, use "OPTION A" below
     - If it has existing <ul> with <li> entries, use "OPTION B" below

  OPTION A: FILE IS EMPTY (no existing tabs)
  ==========================================
  If the file is empty or nearly empty, copy the ENTIRE code block below:

  ---START COPY HERE---
  <ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
    <li class="nav-item">
      <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#chargen-inklings-pane">Secret &amp; Goal</a>
    </li>
  </ul>
  ---END COPY---

  OPTION B: FILE ALREADY HAS TABS (existing custom chargen tabs)
  ============================================================
  If the file already has a <ul> with other <li> entries:

  1. Find the <ul> element that contains chargen step tabs
  2. Look for the closing </ul> tag
  3. Copy just the <li> block below (between the markers)
  4. Paste it inside the <ul>, right before the </ul> closing tag
  5. Save the file

  ---START COPY HERE---
  <li class="nav-item">
    <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#chargen-inklings-pane">Secret &amp; Goal</a>
  </li>
  ---END COPY---

  IMPORTANT: DO NOT change the href="#chargen-inklings-pane"
  It must match the id="chargen-inklings-pane" in chargen-custom.snippet.hbs

  IF YOU CUSTOMIZED chargen_required_types:
  If your game uses different inkling types, change the tab label to match.
  Example: if chargen_required_types: [hooks], change "Secret &amp; Goal" to "Hooks"

  BEFORE (secret and goal):
    <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#chargen-inklings-pane">Secret &amp; Goal</a>

  AFTER (hooks):
    <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#chargen-inklings-pane">Hooks</a>

  Note: Keep href="#chargen-inklings-pane" and id="chargen-inklings-pane" the same,
        only change the display label to match your configured types.
}}
